[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "コンコン！　貴殿の心にお邪魔しまする！\nキツネの鬼門にございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00556",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "絶対一番、ナンバーワン！　ハムスターのヨハナよ。\nネズミじゃないから、覚えておいて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00557",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ねこじゃらしよりハンマー！　イザナだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00558",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00559",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00560",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00561",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "動物の世界からやって来た、\n猪突猛進の新生アイドルとは拙者たちのこと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00562",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "歌とダンスに自信あり。\n気付けばその目が奪われている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00563",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "みんなに笑顔と癒しと愛を届けるよ！\nこれからのアタシたちを見ていってね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00564",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "どう？　それっぽく編集してみたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00565",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "動画投稿サイトにそのままアップされていても\n遜色ないかと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00566",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "さすがはハイディ殿。技術面は心配ありませんな。\n内容についても意見をいただけると助かりまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00567",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "んー、そうだなあ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00568",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "鬼門は場数を踏んでるのかな？　動画の中でも\n明るくて、視聴者受けが良さそうに感じたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00569",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "イザナも物怖じしてないし、\n天真爛漫さが出てていいと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00570",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "ヨハナは……あんた、もしかしてクールで売ってるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00571",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "な、何よ。なんか文句あるの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00572",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "いや、なんというか……\n不愛想に見られちゃうかもなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00573",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "確かに、ヨハナってライブのときとかだけ\nクールになるよね。なんで？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00574",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんでって……そういうキャラでいこうって\n思っただけよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00575",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ふーん？　いつものヨハナも面白いって思うけどなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00576",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんたが私をどう思ってるかよーく分かったわ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00577",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "わあ！　怒らないで！　怒らないで！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00578",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "とにかく、素の私を観客に見せるなんて嫌。\nあれが私の理想の……かっこいいアイドルの姿なの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00579",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "変えるつもりなんてないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00580",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まあ、全員元気系というのも味がないし、\nある意味バランスが取れているとも言えましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00581",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ダンスと歌が完璧な、クール美少女。\nヨハナはその方向で売っていくでござるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00582",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "525253414527026735",
		"text": "なるほどね。じゃ、問題ないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_504_00583",
		"still_path_hash": "8455600619670167820",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "要領も分かってきたし、色々な動画を\n撮ってみようよ！　ハンマーは熱いうちに打て！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00584",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "もうネタは考えてるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00585",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それは、これからだけどぉ……\n街を色々回ってみれば、何か思い浮かぶかも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00586",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そうね。ずっと教室で頭を使ってたし、\n外の空気を吸いたいわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00587",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "では、ネタ探しも兼ねて外を回るといたしましょう。\nとにかく今は、質よりも量でありまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00588",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "おー！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00589",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]